</ol>
<h3 id='edit_content'>Edit content</h3>
<p>You can only edit content that you have added to the Practitioner notes To edit content on the Practitioner Notes:</p>
<ol>
<li>Click <strong>ACTIONS</strong> &gt; <strong>Edit Page</strong>.
<ol>
<li>While editing the page, you can also add the page to a version you want. By default, the previously added version is selected. Select the version and click <strong>Edit</strong>.</li>
<li>If you don't want to add a version, click <strong>Skip</strong>.</li>
</ol></li>
<li>In the editor, make the changes you want.</li>
<li>Click <strong>SAVE</strong> to save your changes.</li>
<li>To publish the updated page, assign the page for review.</li>
</ol>
<h3 id='delete_content'>Delete content</h3>
<p>You can only delete the content that you have added to the Practitioner notes. To delete the content:</p>
<ol>
<li>Click <strong>ACTIONS</strong> &gt; <strong>Delete this page</strong>.</li>
<li>Confirm the action.</li>
</ol>